{"tid":488453,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)石破天驚 衝出寧靜號","createTime":"2017-12-03T17:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T20:00:23.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f0a548d61f59f705c5d3411900d9fcfd5e6716cd","tid":488453,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T17:23:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=FoUqEXIYCekD%2FWcRzGgbQywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=fbfc81a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=FoUqEXIYCekD%2FWcRzGgbQywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=6dc3cc3e\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/danlkaelb/1320245400-901803871.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fdanlkaelb%2F1320245400-901803871.jpg&h=d94dd39e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://bandbent.files.wordpress.com/2010/01/serenity.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbandbent.files.wordpress.com%2F2010%2F01%2Fserenity.jpg&h=b953b8c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.在1963年以前，位於舊金山外海的惡魔島以嚴密的警衛措施，成為全美犯人聞之喪膽的魔鬼監獄，固若金湯的天牢設計，讓重刑犯如同囚禁在銅牆鐵壁之中。監獄廢棄後，惡魔島成了觀光勝地，每日都有遊客湧進其中，嘗試坐牢的滋味。然而此時惡魔島卻落在一群軍人的手裡，成為他們臨時的基地<br />\n<br />\n2.本片劇情大約發生在電視劇《螢火蟲》最後一集的兩個月後[2]。《衝出寧靜號》講述五百年後的未來，一群駕駛太空運輸船的艦長和船員的冒險故事。艦長和大副參與過「聯合戰爭」（Unification War），後來戰敗。他們讓一位具超自然能力，懷有危險機密的乘客上船後，從此逍遙自在、小罪小過的生活就煙消雲散..<br />\n<br />\n1 30AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=FoUqEXIYCekD%2FWcRzGgbQywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=1e2dccab\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=FoUqEXIYCekD%2FWcRzGgbQywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=a814b616\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee615f9e1a75f5bfbd78a8ea9b71dcc41655e357","tid":488453,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T17:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1eb3ae7145bb21294aa85ba526851478603ba20","tid":488453,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T18:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f818e70a6f7a1b634dd18f6ca83971f5b666687","tid":488453,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T18:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87bc2f2892e446c713b62678d76772564094e2d7","tid":488453,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T19:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hk